*Epizoda* je bila zanimljiva i zabavna. (The episode was interesting and entertaining.)

*Epizoda* se završila neočekivano. (The episode ended unexpectedly.)

Bilo je mnogo zanimljivih *epizoda* u toj seriji. (There were many interesting episodes in that series.)

Ona je odigrala glavnu *epizodu* u filmu. (She played the main episode in the movie.)

Oni su imali nekoliko *epizoda* u svojoj seriji. (They had several episodes in their series.)